## 3. Design Tokens

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| Gold (active text, checkmark) | `#d4af37` | Active option, check icon |
| Trigger background | `rgba(19, 20, 15, 0.7)` | Glassmorphic dark |
| Trigger border | `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08)` | Subtle border |
| Trigger border hover | `rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)` | Gold hint on hover |
| Trigger border open | `rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4)` | Gold when open |
| Menu background | `rgba(19, 20, 15, 0.92)` | Darker glass |
| Menu border | `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)` | Subtle border |
| Option hover bg | `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06)` | Very subtle highlight |
| Flag size | `20×14px` | Standard across all |
| Label font | `0.68rem / 700 / uppercase / 0.06em` | Consistent typography |
| Border radius trigger | `8px` | Rounded corners |
| Border radius options | `6px` | Slightly smaller |
| Backdrop blur trigger | `12px` | Glass effect |
| Backdrop blur menu | `16px` | Stronger glass |

